#command name : arguments : Description : See also
text font available: :List text fonts available.:text font
text font:a[<id no> [<string>]]:Create, list or delete fonts:text place, text font available
text help: :List help for text commands:help
text place align:[<id no> (left | center | right) (top | middle | bottom) [<rotation>]:Set alignment for placed text:text place, text alpha, text coor, text rotation:text place, text place alpha, text place clipabs, text place clip, text place coor, text place font, text place grow, text place rgb, text place rotation, text place scale, text place string
text place alpha:[<id no> <alpha>]:Set or list alpha for placed text:text place, text place align, text place alpha, text place clipabs, text place clip, text place coor, text place font, text place grow, text place rgb, text place rotation, text place scale, text place string
text place backgr clip:[<place id> <clip left> <clip right> <clip top> <clip bottom>]:Set or list clip parameter for background of placed text:text place backgr, text place backgr clip, text place backgr linpat, text place backgr round
text place backgr:[<id no> [ <l_pad> <r_pad> <t_pad> <b_pad> [<red> <green> <blue> <alpha>]]]:Set, list or delete background for placed text:text place backgr, text place backgr clip, text place backgr linpat, text place backgr round
text place backgr linpat:[<place_id> [<fraction> <red> <green> <blue> <alpha>] [ v | h]]:Set, list or delete linear pattern background for placed text:Set, list or delete background for placed text:text place backgr, text place backgr clip, text place backgr linpat, text place backgr round
text place backgr move alpha:[<id no> <delta alpha> <alpha steps>]:Set animation parameters for alpha for text background for placed text:text place, text place backgr, text place backgr movealpha, text place backgr move clip,
text place backgr move clip:[<place id> <delta left> <delta right> <delta top> <delta bottom> <left steps> <right steps> <top steps> <bottom steps>]:Set animation parameters for clip for text background for placed text:text place, text place backgr, text place backgr movealpha, text place backgr move clip
text place backgr round:[<place id> <left top> <right top> <left bottom> <right bottom>]:Set round corners for text background for placed text:Set, list or delete background for placed text:text place backgr, text place backgr clip, text place backgr linpat, text place backgr round
text place clipabs:[<place id> <clip x> <clip y> <clip width> <clip height>]:Set clipping absolute for placed text:text place, text place alpha, text place clipabs, text place clip, text place coor, text place font, text place grow, text place rgb, text place rotation, text place scale, text place string
text place clip:[<place id> <clip left> <clip right> <clip top> <clip bottom>]:Set clipping relative for placed text:text place, text place alpha, text place clipabs, text place clip, text place coor, text place font, text place grow, text place rgb, text place rotation, text place scale, text place string
text place coor:[<place_id> <x> <y>]:Change coordinates for placed text:text place, text place alpha, text place clipabs, text place clip, text place coor, text place font, text place grow, text place rgb, text place rotation, text place scale, text place string
text place font:[<id no> <font id>]:Change font ID for placed text:text place, text place alpha, text place clipabs, text place clip, text place coor, text place font, text place grow, text place rgb, text place rotation, text place scale, text place string
text place grow:<id no> <start len> [<delta grow> [variable]]:Set the part of the string of placed text that is displayed to grow:text place, text place alpha, text place clipabs, text place clip, text place coor, text place font, text place grow, text place rgb, text place rotation, text place scale, text place string
text place:[<id no> [ <text_id> <font_id> <x> <y>[<red> <green> <blue> [ <alpha> [ nw | ne | se | sw | n | s | e | w ]]]]]:Set, list or delete placed text:text place, text place alpha, text place clipabs, text place clip, text place coor, text place font, text place grow, text place rgb, text place rotation, text place scale, text place string
text place move alpha:[<place id> <delta_alpha> <step_alpha>]:Set animation for alpha for placed text:text place, text place move alpha, text place move clip, text place move coor, text place move rotation, text place move scale
text place move clip:[<id no> <delta left> <delta right> <delta top> <delta bottom> <left steps> <right steps> <top steps> <bottom steps>]:Set animation for clipping of text:text place, text place move alpha, text place move clip, text place move coor, text place move rotation, text place move scale
text place move coor:[<place id> [<delta_x> <delta_y> <step_x> <step_y>]]:Set animation for coordinates of placed text:text place, text place move alpha, text place move clip, text place move coor, text place move rotation, text place move scale
text place move rotation:[<place id> <delta_rotation> <step_rotation>]:Set animation for rotation of placed text:text place, text place move alpha, text place move clip, text place move coor, text place move rotation, text place move scale
text place move scale:[<place id> <delta_scale_x> <delta_scale_y> <step_x> <step_y>]:Set animation for scale of placed text:text place, text place move alpha, text place move clip, text place move coor, text place move rotation, text place move scale
text place repeat move:[<id no> <dx> <dy> <end x> <end y>]:Set a repeated animation of the coordinates for placed text:
text place rgb:[<id no> <red> <green> <blue>]:Change or list the color of a placed text:text place, text place alpha, text place clipabs, text place clip, text place coor, text place font, text place grow, text place rgb, text place rotation, text place scale, text place string
text place rotation:[<id no> <rotation>]:Change or list rotation of placed text:text place, text place alpha, text place clipabs, text place clip, text place coor, text place font, text place grow, text place rgb, text place rotation, text place scale, text place string
text place scale:[<id no> <scale_x> <scale_y>]:Change or list scale of placed text:text place, text place alpha, text place clipabs, text place clip, text place coor, text place font, text place grow, text place rgb, text place rotation, text place scale, text place string
text place string:[<id no> <string id>]:Change or list the string IDs associated with placed text:text place, text place alpha, text place clipabs, text place clip, text place coor, text place font, text place grow, text place rgb, text place rotation, text place scale, text place string
text string concat:<dest string id> <string id> [<string id> ...]:Concatenate two defined strings of text:text string, text place, text place string
text string:[<id no> [<string>]]:Create, list or delete strings of text:text place, text place string
